                   about the hour of seven in the night, on the <rs id="t17940430-33-cd168" type="crimeDate">first of March</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17940430-33-off167 t17940430-33-cd168"></join>, and burglariously stealing therein, four fancy rings, set in gold, value 1l. 10s. and three fancy lockits, set in gold, value 3l. the goods of the said 
                     <persName id="t17940430-33-person345">
                        John 
                        Stubbs
                     <interp inst="t17940430-33-person345" type="surname" value="Stubbs"></interp>
